data.description: MOVE IN CONDITION! RANCH HOUSE -- FULL REHAB /  RENOVATED -- ONLY $607/YEAR TAX -- PITI PAYMENTS AROUND $1200 -- LESS THAN  RENT -- BEATS THE NEXT CLOSEST LISTING BY $300/MONTH FOR 30 YEARS!!-- QUICK  CLOSE POSSIBLE ! CURRENT CERTIFICATE OF OCCUPANCY ON FILE -- CONTACT  LISTING AGENT DIRECT OR SIGN FOR OWNERS NUMBER AND SAVE $$$$$ This fully  renovated ranch-style home, meticulously stripped to the studs, introduces an entirely NEW  living experience. Every aspect, from plumbing and electric to insulation and flooring, is  meticulously updated. Permitted and inspected by a trusted construction company since  2005, this home embodies quality. Inside, discover a home thoughtfully designed with 1stfloor laundry and bedrooms for effortless living. The bathroom boasts NEW ceramic tiles  with elegant designs, complemented by high-end stainless steel faucets and a rejuvenating  showerhead. Granite countertops seamlessly flow from the kitchen to the bathroom,  unifying the space with sophistication. Enjoy the ease of energy-efficient lighting, adaptable  with cold/warm light settings throughout. Experience the spacious layout, enhanced by  exterior stove exhaust and NEW cabinets, offering both style and functionality. A dedicated  laundry area not only provides convenience but also ample space for pantry items. Step  outside through sliding doors to a large fenced yard, a perfect retreat. The exterior  showcases a unique front door and striking LP Siding, adding character to your home. Stay  connected with a NEW wifi-enabled garage door for modern living. In addition, benefit from  NEW gutters, windows, water heater, furnace, and AC unit, ensuring efficiency and comfort  year-round. Roomy closets in all bedrooms cater to your storage needs. Your ideal home  awaits, offering not just a place to live, but a lifestyle redefined. Plus, enjoy the advantage  of Low Low Taxes, making this home an exceptional opportunity.
